enerative-ai-161749404.html"><ins>谷歌照片更新通过生成人工智能改进了记忆视图</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/googles-latest-ai-trick-is-summarizing-long-web-pages-160004700.html"><ins>谷歌最新的人工智能技巧是总结长网页</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/logitechs-litra-glow-streaming-light-drops-back-down-to-50-164650143.html"><ins>罗技 Litra Glow 流光灯降价至 50 美元</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-music-debuts-samples-a-tiktok-style-feed-for-music-discovery-160007555.html"><ins>YouTube Music 推出 Samples，这是一种用于音乐发现的 TikTok 风格的提要</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/government-warrant-search-phone-cloud-fourth-amendment-legal-191533735.html"><ins>让政府搜查你手机的法律漏洞</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/astronomers-confirm-maisies-galaxy-is-one-of-the-oldest-observed-205246905.html"><ins>天文学家证实梅西星系是观测到的最古老的星系之一</ins></a></p><h2><a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lamborghini-teases-a-fully-electric-supercar-ahead-of-its-august-18th-reveal-201059772.html"><ins>兰博基尼在 8 月 18 日发布前预告了一款全电动超级跑车</ins></a></h2><h3>看起来很漂亮，笼罩在阴影中。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/lamborghini-teases-a-fully-electric-supercar-ahead-of-its-august-18th-reveal-201059772.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8174fcf0-3c1d-11ee-afcd-b84461763996" style="height:352px;width:625px;" alt="新款兰博基尼电动车的图像笼罩在阴影中，只能看到车顶线。" data-uuid="a2dd54eb-5554-3f09-820f-c1974c015b4a"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">兰博基尼</div></figure></a><p>8 月 18 日，兰博基尼预计将推出其首款全电动超级（超？巨型？）概念车。在活动之前，该<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lamborghini-teases-a-fully-electric-supercar-ahead-of-its-august-18th-reveal-201059772.html"><ins>公司发布了这个预告片，展示了该模型非常干净的线条。</ins></a>细节很少，但我们确实知道这将是一款全新的车辆，而不是现有鞭子的电动版本。您将有时间存钱购买一件；我们预计几年内不会看到适合公路行驶的版本。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href=