hone-android-160056147.html"><ins>2023 年 Apple Music Lossless 最佳 DAC</ins></a></h2><h3>随时随地获取 HiFi 音频。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-dac-for-lossless-high-resolution-music-iphone-android-160056147.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/1a5e57e0-3c1e-11ee-bbdf-8166898cac9d" style="height:417px;width:625px;" alt="木桌上的一系列便携式 DAC 以及 iPhone 屏幕和一副耳机的图像。" data-uuid="417f125b-14f8-3988-8fcc-ed61b34c7a32"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">詹姆斯·特鲁 / Engadget 摄</div></figure></a><p>苹果对高分辨率音频的迟来的拥抱意味着人们对如何充分利用其音频服务更加感兴趣。声音专家 James Trew 整理了<a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-dac-for-lossless-high-resolution-music-iphone-android-160056147.html"><ins>这份最佳 DAC 指南，无论在家中还是在旅途中都能提供清晰的音频</ins></a>。他还添加了与 Qobuz、Tidal 和 Deezer 配合良好的选项（如果您对这些音乐有忠诚度的话）。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-dac-for-lossless-high-resolution-music-iphone-android-160056147.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-is-slowing-down-links-to-websites-elon-musk-has-publicly-feuded-with-185544463.html"><ins>X正在减慢与埃隆·马斯克公开不和的网站的链接</ins></a></h2><h3>因为当然有。</h3><p></p><p> Xwitter 似乎有意<a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-is-slowing-down-links-to-websites-elon-musk-has-publicly-feuded-with-185544463.html"><ins>放慢与其创始人不喜欢的竞争对手平台和组织的出站链接</ins></a>。最近几天，用户点击<em>《纽约时报》</em> 、Mastodon、Bluesky、Threads 和 Substack 的链接时都出现了五秒的延迟。目标清单以及延迟实施的一致性表明，这是故意试图掩盖马斯克愤怒的目标。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-is-slowing-down-links-to-websites-elon-musk-has-publicly-feuded-with-185544463.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-tesla-offers-cheaper-model-s-and-model-x-options-with-shorter-range-111540531.html ?src=rss]]>; </descri