-24-twitter-mulls-paid-tweetdeck.html">在 2017 年询问用户</a>是否愿意每月支付 20 美元以获得“更高级的 TweetDeck 体验”。这一新举措是埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 尝试通过 Blue 订阅从该应用程序中获利的一部分，但截至去年 6 月，该服务仅拥有约<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/elon-musk-twitter-sharing-revenue-creators-ads-replies/652645/">70 万订阅者</a>。马斯克还誓言要使 X 成为一款“ <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-is-rebranding-twitter-to-x-and-killing-the-bird-logo-165944573.html">一切应用程序</a>”，用于社交网络上的内容创建、支付和购物。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tweetdeck-now-requires-a-paid-subscription-082209535.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tweetdeck-now-requires-a-paid-subscription-082209535.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 074403de-2ee7-4e0b-a6e7-cbb21c6b9f8d</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 16 Aug 2023 08:22:09 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692174130</ingested><modified> 2023-08-16T08:22:13+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="3333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/9a428640-3c08-11ee-b39f-91e313c2cbbe" width="5000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/9a428640-3c08-11ee-b39f-91e313c2cbbe" width="5000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Carlos Barria / reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA['X' logo is seen on the top of the headquarters of the messaging platform X, formerly known as Twitter, in downtown San Francisco, California, U.S., July 30, 2023. REUTERS/Carlos Barria]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[TWITTER-MUSK/X SIGN]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[January 6th riot investigators obtained Trump's Twitter DMs and deleted posts]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>尽管从 Twitter（现为 X）获取前总统唐纳德·特朗普的记录<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-fined-for-belatedly-complying-with-search-warrant-for-donald-trumps-account-173745495.html">遇到了麻烦</a>，但调查 2020 年 1 月 6 日事件的特别检察官最终还是从该网站获得了大量信息。不过，根据<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.politico.com/news/2023/08/15/special-counsel-obtained-trump-twitter-howell-00111410"><em>Politico</em></a>分享的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.dcd.uscourts.gov/sites/dcd/files/23sc31%20Attachment%20A%20-%20Documents%20unsealed%20with%20redactions.pdf">新近公开的法庭文件</a>(PDF)，律师经过了多次来回和巨大的努力才能够获得 Twitter 请求的数据。</p><p>显然，搜查令要求 Twitter 提供 @realdonaldtrump 创建、起草、点赞或转发的所有推文，包括他最终删除的任何帖子。该网站还必须交出@realdonaldtrump“以草稿形式发送、接收、存储或以其他方式与@realdonaldtrump相关的私信”，以及前总统可能在同一设备上使用过的与之相关的所有其他帐户。用于登录 @realdonaldtrump 的所有设备都必须记录下来并提供给律师，以及该帐户的隐私设置和 2020 年 10 月至 2021 年 1 月期间的 IP 地址历史记录。此外，Twitter 还必须移交所有记录@realdonaldtrump 进行的搜索以及同一时间段内帐户的位置信息。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>在整个诉讼记录中，你会看到检察官如何坚持要求推特必须遵守保密令，禁止该公司向特朗普透露逮捕令。他们解释说，他们有证据表明披露搜查令可能会危及调查，并警告法庭“对于调查和证人的后续调查来说，将会造成实际的伤害和担忧。”与此同时，推特方面辩称，调查人员要求的一些信息可能属于行政特权，检察官和法官对此提出质疑，因为他们认为特朗普不太可能通过私信讨论官方政府事务。</p><p>据<em>《Politico》</em>报道，美国地区法官贝丽尔·豪厄尔（Beryl Howell）特别提请人们关注推特为特朗普提前发出有关搜查令的通知所做的努力。她称这一行动“非同寻常”，是该公司从未为其他用户做过的事情。法官想知道埃隆·马斯克是否试图“讨好”这位前总统，让他在这个平台上感到“特别受欢迎”。马斯克接管该网站后，特朗普的推特账户已经<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-donald-trump-unbanned-elon-musk-023043690.html">恢复</a>，但他尚未再次开始发帖。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/january-6th-riot-investigators-obtained-trumps-twitter-dms-and-deleted-posts-064330362.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/january-6th-riot-investigators-obtained-trumps-twitter-dms-and-deleted-posts-064330362.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c0c7ca19-f41e-4d4c-bfe8-3f570d295923</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 16 Aug 2023 06:43:30 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692168198</ingested><modified> 2023-08-16T06:43:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="2403" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/984403b0-3bf3-11ee-96ff-9b967cee9b12" width="3600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2403" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/984403b0-3bf3-11ee-96ff-9b967cee9b12" width="3600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[zz/KGC-375/STAR MAX/IPx]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[AUGUST 14th 2023: Former President of The United States of America Donald Trump is indicted by a special purpose grand jury criminally charging Trump and his allies of racketeering and conspiracy in their efforts to overturn the 2020 presidential election results in the state of Georgia. - File Photo by: zz/KGC-375/STAR MAX/IPx 2019 6/5/19 President of The United States Donald Trump joined dignitaries and military veterans in Portsmouth, England on June 5, 2019 to commemorate the 75th Anniversary of the D-Day Invasion in June of 1944 during World War II. (Portsmouth, England, UK)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Donald Trump indicted in Georgia 2020 election interference case]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>